commit c0d5e58eb817a0ed54aab1d9e52c68ae4ac7f73e
Author: Sebastian Utz <su@rtme.net>
Date:   Mon Nov 17 17:57:32 2025 +0100

    Fix memory based pause/resume of the sharding executor.
    
    Ensures that pause/resume will work even when no target node
    statistics like RTT are yet available.
    
    Fixes #18130.
    
    (cherry picked from commit a2f572fc480380b3c2d17fd3b5e436e759723c19)

